Recommended Stack with Express:
•  Database: pg or pg-promise for PostgreSQL queries (Tasks 1.1, 2.3, 4.1, 5.1).
•  Payments: stripe SDK (Task 2.1).
•  PDF Generation: pdfkit (Task 3.2).
•  Email: nodemailer with @sendgrid/mail (Task 3.3).
•  CSV Export: csv-writer (Task 5.2).
•  Environment: dotenv for API keys.
•  Security: helmet for HTTP headers, express-rate-limit for API protection.
•  Testing: jest and supertest for endpoint testing (Task 4.2).
•  Deployment: AWS EC2 with S3 for photo storage, Docker for consistency.
